GET {{host}}/api/orders?dateFrom=2026-01-01&dateTo=2026-12-31
Accept: application/json

### Get orders with combined filters
GET {{host}}/api/orders?studentId=1&status=InProgress
Accept: application/json

### Get order by ID
GET {{host}}/api/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Get order summary (financial)
GET {{host}}/api/orders/1/summary
Accept: application/json

