POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "notes": "Fotos para graduación"
}

### Update order (notes only)
PUT {{host}}/api/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Actualización de notas del pedido"
}

